{"tid":1347300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Fact Check] 傳元朗事件傷者有孕婦　醫管局：未收過孕婦或流產個案","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:05:34.000Z","uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1470c66af99f94471959f3f619678e312dcb6a7","tid":1347300,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:08.000Z","msg":"傳元朗事件傷者有孕婦　醫管局：未收過孕婦或流產個案<br />\n<br />\n一批穿著白衣的人士，昨晚進入西鐵元朗站內，用木棍、藤條等襲擊市民和乘客。截至早上7時，傷者人數上升至45人，其中一名男子危殆。對於有傳言，指傷者包括孕婦，醫管局發言人回覆查詢時說，公立醫院急症室未有接收過任何孕婦或流產個案，並呼籲有需要的病人適時求診。<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-22 13:36:10<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469730-20190722.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469730-20190722.htm&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=f3ad02b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469730-20190722.htm&h=0bb01eb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469730-20190722.htm</a>"},{"pid":"95322d14c330ddd96f7d68b78bd7c3efd5f32fad","tid":1347300,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"但係HA 都唔係咁信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9e9581fecefc9bca8eac5f12e6e493d18f403b","tid":1347300,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"當住係Good news 先?"},{"pid":"6cdd36b613b3c67611fda2568945ad37746ee1fb","tid":1347300,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:52:57.000Z","msg":"見過有whatsapp cap 圖話係ICU，更有消息指留左產，不過無save 低"},{"pid":"146412c0d8abb106a57d41810cfc55f0a26027eb","tid":1347300,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8520851f5f2910fb7bcc8d842e9d970fc9cd6f0","tid":1347300,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB